OL,3,CMan denies murdering mother and her
OL,4,Cthree children in a house fire
OL,6,FA man has denied murdering a mother
OL,7,Fand her three children in a house fire.
OL,9,FBryonie Gawith, 29, nine-year-old
OL,10,FDenisty Birtle, five-year-old Oscar
OL,11,FBirtle and 22-month-old Aubree Birtle
OL,12,Fdied after the blaze at their home in
OL,13,FWestbury Road, Bradford, in the early
OL,14,Fhours of August 21 last year.
OL,16,FSharaz Ali, 39, of no fixed address,
OL,17,Fis charged with murdering the family,
OL,18,Fas well as attempting to murder Ms
OL,19,FGawith's sister Antonia Gawith.
