OL,3,CMan denies murdering mother and her
OL,4,Cthree children in a house fire
OL,6,FOn Monday, he pleaded not guilty at
OL,7,FBradford Crown Court to all five
OL,8,Fcharges, as well as a charge of
OL,9,Fattempting to cause grievous bodily
OL,10,Fharm to Antonia Gawith.
OL,12,FAli is one of three men due to go on
OL,13,Ftrial accused of murdering Ms Gawith
OL,14,Fand her three children.
OL,16,FMohammed Shabir, 44, of Alice Street,
OL,17,FKeighley; and Calum Sunderland, 25, of
OL,18,FCalton Street, Keighley pleaded not
OL,19,Fguilty to the charges in September
OL,20,Flast year.
