OL,3,CMan denies murdering mother and her
OL,4,Cthree children in a house fire
OL,6,FEarlier hearings have been told that
OL,7,FAli had been in a coma since the fire
OL,8,Fand was not expected to be well enough
OL,9,Fto stand trial, even if he did wake up.
OL,11,FHis prognosis was later revised and,
OL,12,Ffollowing a "marked improvement" in
OL,13,Fhis condition at the beginning of this
OL,14,Fyear, Ali was charged with the
OL,15,Foffences in March after doctors found
OL,16,Fhim fit to stand trial.
OL,18,FHe appeared at his first court
OL,19,Fhearings via video link from his
OL,20,Fhospital bed, before being moved to
OL,21,Fprison.
