OL,6,FThe three defendants appeared together
OL,7,Fremotely from prison at Monday's
OL,8,Fhearing, when prosecutor David Brooke
OL,9,FKC said Ali "does appear to be fit".
OL,11,FTheir trial is expected to go ahead on
OL,12,FNovember 17, the court heard.
